# Presentation Layer

## Controllers
- HTTP concerns only
- Extract to DTOs immediately
- Call services, no logic
- Standardized responses

## DTOs
- All API inputs/outputs
- Validate before business layer
- No business logic

## Routes
- Organize by resource
- RESTful conventions
- Version APIs

## Middleware
- Auth/authz
- Request logging
- Error handling
- Rate limiting

## Responses
- Consistent structure
- No internal error exposure
- Appropriate HTTP status codes
